title: O'NEILL PSYCHOFREAK 2011/12
description: O'Neill's new XDS-Air Firewall is more insulating and water wicking than ever. We've put this state-of-the-art insulation in the chest, back and in the lower core panels. With the all new Triple XDS in the arms, shoulders, and lower legs add flex and durability where you need it most. Psychofreak takes you beyond warm, beyond flexible and beyond your imagination.
